# repositories/
#
# Data-access layer. Each file handles reads/writes for one domain.
# In Phase 2, these will wrap the MITRA API client (and later, the database).
#
# Phase 2 repositories to create:
#   busRepository.js    — fetches vehicle GPS data from MITRA
#   routeRepository.js  — fetches route metadata
#   stopRepository.js   — fetches stop details
#
# Convention:
#   - Repositories return raw data or throw ApiError
#   - Services transform raw data into domain objects
#   - Controllers never call repositories directly
